Kubernetes Updates:-

I have completed basic opertaion like:

-Create a yaml file containing the pod spec for the nginx pod.
-Create the pod.
-Verify the pod has been created or not
-Create yaml file to create replicaset
-Scale up and down the replicas

Below are the commands which i have used while doing lab:

kubectl get nodes
kubectl get pods
kubectl run nginx --image=nginx
kubectl get pods -o wide
kubectl get replicaset
kubectl describe pod newpods-bqkbm | grep -i image
kubectl get pods -o wide
kubectl get pods webapp
kubectl run redis --image=redis123 --dry-run=client -o yaml > pod.yaml
kubectl apply -f pod.yaml
kubectl edit pods redis

